The paper also discusses the use of meta parameter learning and compatible skill specifications, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the system using experimental data, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV).
